trans-unit.source: Maintains the collection of sub-properties of a given parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Mantém a coleção de subpropriedades de um determinado pai <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection"></xref> class using the sub-properties of the specified <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection.ParentValue*> instance.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection"> </xref> classe usando as propriedades de subsistema especificada <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection.ParentValue*>instância.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntryCollection.ParentValue*>

trans-unit.source: The parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> instance used for the initialization.
trans-unit.target: O pai <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> usada para a inicialização de instância.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances in this collection (typically the number of sub-properties for the parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref>).
trans-unit.target: Obtém o número de <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"> </xref> instâncias desta coleção (normalmente o número de subpropriedades pai <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref>).

trans-unit.source: An integer that specifies the number of instances in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Um inteiro que especifica o número de instâncias na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator> object that iterates all the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator>objeto que itera todas as <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"> </xref> instâncias nesta coleção.</xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601> that can be used to iterate through the collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerator%601> que pode ser usado para iterar através da coleção de <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"> </xref> instâncias.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instance with the specified name from this collection.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"> </xref> instância com o nome especificado desta coleção.

trans-unit.source: It is used for sub-property retrieval.
trans-unit.target: Ele é usado para recuperação de propriedades do sub.

trans-unit.source: The name of the property to get.
trans-unit.target: O nome da propriedade a ser obtida.

trans-unit.source: A property entry instance with the specified name; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> if it does not exist.
trans-unit.target: Uma instância de entrada de propriedade com o nome especificado. ou <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> se ele não existe.

trans-unit.source: Gets the parent <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"></xref> from the host infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o pai <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyValue"> </xref> da infraestrutura de host.

trans-unit.source: Returns an <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator> object that iterates all of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator>objeto que itera todas as <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"> </xref> instâncias nesta coleção.</xref:Systems.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> object that can be used to iterate through collection of <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"></xref> instances.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>objeto que pode ser usado para iterar pela coleção de <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.PropertyEditing.PropertyEntry"> </xref> instâncias.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>
